  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Deserialization_JsonDeserializer'>Class JsonDeserializer    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Deserialization/JsonDeserializer.cs#L41'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Deserializes JSON strings into objects.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public sealed class JsonDeserializer : IJsonDeserializer</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.html'>JsonDeserializer</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.IJsonDeserializer.html'>IJsonDeserializer</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.#ctor(Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.#ctor(Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Deserialization_JsonDeserializer__ctor_Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Parsing_IJsonParser_'>JsonDeserializer(IJsonParser)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Deserialization/JsonDeserializer.cs#L53'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> class.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public JsonDeserializer(IJsonParser jsonParser)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>jsonParser</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.html'>IJsonParser</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The JSON parser to use.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Exceptions</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.argumentnullexception'>ArgumentNullException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when jsonParser is null.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer._jsonParser' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer._jsonParser' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Deserialization_JsonDeserializer__jsonParser'>_jsonParser    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Deserialization/JsonDeserializer.cs#L46'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The json parser</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private readonly IJsonParser _jsonParser</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.html'>IJsonParser</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.Deserialize``1(System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.Deserialize``1(System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Deserialization_JsonDeserializer_Deserialize__1_System_String_'>Deserialize&lt;T&gt;(string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Deserialization/JsonDeserializer.cs#L63'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Deserializes a JSON string into an object of the specified type.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>[ExcludeFromCodeCoverage]\npublic T Deserialize&lt;T&gt;(string json) where T : IJsonSerializable, IJsonDesSerializable&lt;T&gt;, new()</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>json</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The JSON string to deserialize.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">An instance of the specified type populated with data from the JSON.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The target type, which must implement IJsonSerializable and IJsonDesSerializable&lt;T&gt;.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Exceptions</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.argumentnullexception'>ArgumentNullException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when json is null.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Exceptions.JsonDeserializationException.html'>JsonDeserializationException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.JsonDeserializer.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when deserialization fails.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
